{
  "id": "10027",
  "key": "GG-24",
  "fields": {
    "summary": "Design JSON Schema for Exported Jira Issues, Workflows, Screens, and Custom Fields",
    "description": {
      "type": "doc",
      "version": 1,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Use case:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "As a "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "member of Team Gamma",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", I want to design a JSON schema for the exported Jira issues, workflows, screens, and custom fields, so that the data can be consumed by other teams for migration to Azure DevOps."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "rule"
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Acceptance criteria:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "GIVEN",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " the need to export Jira data for migration,"
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "WHEN",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " designing the JSON schema,"
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "AND",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " including the necessary information for issues, workflows, screens, and custom fields,"
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "THEN",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "em"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " the schema should be well-structured and documented to facilitate consumption by other teams."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "rule"
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Technical notes:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The JSON schema for exported Jira data should include the following structure:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "orderedList",
          "attrs": {
            "order": 1
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Issues:",
                      "marks": [
                        {
                          "type": "strong"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "bulletList",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Issue type"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Fields (including standard and custom fields)"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Relationships (hierarchical and cross-referencing)"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Workflows:",
                      "marks": [
                        {
                          "type": "strong"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "bulletList",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Workflow definitions"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "States"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Transitions"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "orderedList",
          "attrs": {
            "order": 1
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Screens:",
                      "marks": [
                        {
                          "type": "strong"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "bulletList",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Screen definitions"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Associated fields and configurations"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Custom Fields:",
                      "marks": [
                        {
                          "type": "strong"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "bulletList",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Custom field definitions"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "listItem",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "paragraph",
                          "content": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "text": "Configurations and references"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The schema should also include any mapping references (e.g., old Jira IDs) that can aid in replicating the items in Azure DevOps by "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Team EitanYsusEnemigos",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". Additionally, clear documentation of the schema structure should be provided to ensure ease of understanding and future extendibility if needed."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This schema will be shared with "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Team EitanYsusEnemigos",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Team SinChambaTeam",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to facilitate smooth migration and independent integration of test data."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
